=== Notes ===
- Loss converged smoothly; no instability observed (gamma=0.3 confirmed stable on weak-discriminating pairs)
- gamma=0.5 was tested in a preliminary 1-epoch run: loss oscillated at step 15-25 and eval loss was 0.12 higher at epoch 1
- Training time: ~38 minutes on Colab T4
- Peak VRAM: 13.8 GB (reference-free SimPO vs. ~15.4 GB estimated for DPO — would OOM on T4)
- Adapter size: 47 MB (merged model not created to avoid model_weights/ gitignore conflict)
